# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Nordic Techniques Vocabulary — Linked Data for metadatahub.eu
# 153 entries: techniques used in Nordic museum cataloguing.
#
# Categories: metalworking, textiles, woodworking, ceramics,
# stone/lapidary, painting, printmaking, glass, leather/fibre,
# and Sami/Nordic-specific crafts.
#
# Sources:
#   Getty Art & Architecture Thesaurus (AAT)
#     http://www.getty.edu/research/tools/vocabularies/aat/
#   Wikipedia (various technique articles)
#   Nordic museum cataloguing traditions
#
# Total entries: 153
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

